ZH: 战士们正在基地里待命，随时准备出发。
EN: The soldiers are on standby at the base, ready to deploy at any time.

ZH: 救援队员在灾区待命，随时准备救助被困的居民。
EN: The rescue team is on standby in the disaster area, ready to help the trapped residents.

ZH: 飞机上的乘务员已经做好待命的准备，等待起飞指令。
EN: The flight attendants on the plane are ready for duty, waiting for the takeoff instructions.

ZH: 这台机器人会在需要时待命，执行各种任务。
EN: This robot will be on standby, ready to perform various tasks when needed.

ZH: 比赛前，运动员们在更衣室里做好待命的准备。
EN: Before the game, athletes are getting ready in the locker room, on standby.

ZH: 警察经常在警局里待命，以便随时应对紧急情况。
EN: Police officers often remain on standby at the police station, ready to respond to emergencies at any time.

ZH: 这支队伍已经抵达边境并做好了待命的准备，以防有敌人入侵。
EN: This team has arrived at the border and is prepared to be on standby in case of enemy invasion.

ZH: 在部队，士兵们必须时刻做好待命的准备，以执行各种任务。
EN: In the military, soldiers must always be ready for duty, ready to perform various tasks.

ZH: 教练把队员们集合在一起，做好待命的准备，等待比赛的开始。
EN: The coach gathers the team together, ready for duty, waiting for the start of the game.

ZH: 航天员等待着在太空站里待命，进行科学实验。
EN: Astronauts are waiting to be on standby in the space station for scientific experiments.

ZH: 在医院里，医生和护士必须随时做好待命的准备，处理急诊病例。
EN: In the hospital, doctors and nurses must be ready for duty at all times to handle emergency cases.

ZH: 平时，警车会被停放在适当的位置，进行待命。
EN: Normally, police cars will be parked in proper positions for standby.

ZH: 救护车随时准备着待命，以便从急诊中心接收紧急呼叫。
EN: Ambulances are ready for duty at all times to respond to emergency calls from the emergency center.

ZH: 随着地震的发生，救灾队伍立即做好待命的准备，前往灾区。
EN: With the occurrence of the earthquake, the disaster relief team immediately prepares to be on standby and head to the disaster area.

ZH: 巡逻队员们经常待命在警车里，巡逻街区。
EN: Patrol officers often stay on standby in their patrol cars, patrolling the neighborhood.

ZH: 校园安保人员每天都会在学校里待命，确保师生的安全。
EN: Campus security personnel stay on standby at the school every day to ensure the safety of teachers and students.

ZH: 当敌方进攻时，沿边阵地上的士兵们会立即做好待命的准备，抵御敌人。
EN: When the enemy attacks, soldiers along the border defensive positions immediately prepare to be on standby to resist the enemy.

ZH: 在重大活动期间，消防队员一直留在队站里处于待命状态，以便快速响应。
EN: During major events, firefighters stay in the fire station on standby to respond quickly.

ZH: 医院设有专门的急诊团队，24小时待命，处理各种紧急病例。
EN: Hospitals have dedicated emergency teams on standby 24/7 to handle various urgent medical cases.

ZH: 警方在城市的关键地点设立了待命岗，以确保市民的安全。
EN: The police have set up standby posts at critical locations in the city to ensure the safety of the citizens.
